Step 2) Add CSS:
Example
/* Three columns side by side */
.column {
float: left;
width: 
  33.3%;
margin-bottom: 16px;
padding: 0 8px;
}
/* Display the columns below each other instead of 
  side by side on small screens */
@media screen and (max-width: 650px) {
.column {
width: 100%;
display: block;
}
}
/* Add some shadows to create a card effect */
.card {
box-shadow: 0 4px 8px 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
}
/* Some left and right 
  padding inside the container */
.container {
padding: 0 16px;
}
/* Clear floats */
.container::after, 
  .row::after {
content: "";
clear: both;
display: 
  table;
}
.title {
color: grey;
}
.button {
border: none;
outline: 0;
display: inline-block;
padding: 8px;
color: white;
background-color: #000;
text-align: center;
cursor: pointer;
width: 100%;
}
.button:hover {
background-color: #555;
}

